title: Convenience Concepts Xtra Storage, 1-Door, White
description: If your office needs additional space for office essentials, then the Xtra Storage 1 Door Cabinet by Convenience Concepts will do just that! Made to complete any office or living space, these cabinets are great for storage and even display. Create your own unique design by stacking multiple units side-by-side or give any room dimension by displaying them separately. These versatile cabinets are complete with one open compartment and one closed door compartment. The door also features a chrome knob and a magnetic hinge. Easy assembly with household tools and easy maintenance by wiping clean with a dry cloth. Shop the complete Xtra Storage Door Cabinet Collection by Convenience Concepts, each item sold separately.
